程序包 com.github.deltaquincy.algorithms.collections

类 Stack<Item>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.deltaquincy.algorithms.collections.Stack<Item>
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Iterable<Item>

    public class Stack<Item>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Item>
    The Stack class is a LIFO data structure. In this version, the implementation uses linked list to realize variable length mechanism.

    • 方法详细资料

      • isEmpty

        public boolean isEmpty​()
        Check if the stack is empty.
        返回:
        true if the stack is empty, in other words, its length is 0

      • size

        public int size​()
        Get the current size of the stack.
        返回:
        the current size, or length, of the stack

      • push

        public void push​(Item item)
        Push an item into top of the stack. This would add 1 to the stack length.
        参数:
        item - the item to push into the stack

      • pop

        public Item pop​()
        Pop an item from top of the stack. This would delete the item from the stack and minus 1 to the stack length.
        返回:
        the item just poped from the stack

      • iterator

        public java.util.Iterator<Item> iterator​()
        Implement the iterable interface. For Stack, the iteration would be from the top to the bottom of the stack, corresponding to the LIFO logic.
        指定者:
        iterator 在接口中 java.lang.Iterable<Item>
        返回:
        an appropriate iterator
        另请参阅:
        Iterable, Iterator
